<script type="text/template">
## CGI Diversion

So you can use multiple languages.

I really really really recommend using the CGI library that comes with
your language if you do. Mostly for parsing of GET and POST arguments.

Perl:
````
use CGI;
print CGI->new->header();
````

Python:
````
import cgi
import cgitb
cgitb.enable()
# print your header
````
</script>
</div>
</section>
