<!-- ######################## START MARKDOWN SLIDE ########################## -->
<section>
<div data-markdown>
<script type="text/template">
## CGI Problems

* Slow
* 1 process per invocation
* Ineffecient communication of requests
* Lack of OO representation of a request
* Difficult to share state.

</script>
</div>
</section>
